data.description: Completely renovated home in a gated community with a serene pond off the expansive back deck.  This home boasts so many upgraded features including gas stove, gas tankless water heater, high impact garage door, storm door, extended driveway, new shadowbox fence, and 6 inch gutters around the whole house. As you walk through the front door, you're greeted by an open floorplan living room, kitchen, and dining room. Enjoy Florida breezes and watch tv in the large screened porch just off the kitchen. This home also has a large master with ensuite  bathroom and two other bedrooms with a shared hall bath.
